                    <a name="distribution" id="distribution"><strong>Shipping information</strong></a>
                    <br />
                    Orders received before 12.00 p.m. are usually shipped the same day. Shipping  costs will be calculated in the shopping cart and depend on shipping method,  destination, weight &amp; volume of the goods ordered. &nbsp;<br />
                    We ship in-stock items within  1-2 working days of receipt of your order. We offer a preset selection of  shipping methods: UPS Express Saver (next business day, depending on  destination). UPS Standard (1 to 5 business days in Europe, depending on  destination). Please contact the Customer service desk in case of a speed  delivery.
